         <p>The material in this collection is arranged chronologically. Additions to the collection may vary in arrangement.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_da4b38406ec13c1b392a903d476af08e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of printed material and ephemera relating to political, economic, and social conditions in Rwanda.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
